 purée","2 tsp plain flour","20 g dried porcini mushrooms","100 g red vermouth","350 g water, boiling","1 beef stock cube (for 0.5 l), crumbled","1 tsp fine sea salt, plus 1 pinch","½ tsp ground black pepper, plus 1 pinch","70 g cooked, peeled chestnuts, halved","1 Tbsp unsalted butter","200 g chestnut mushrooms, thinly sliced"]}],"id":"r281772","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/--Zxb916BjLw\/XZQHZBFpYhI\/AAAAAAAAcH4\/Ps-uwe8YBM0unOnqpYHpzKrA786DmR4CwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_iSZJoz78fRclqq0A.png","title":"Pork, Chestnut and Chorizo Stew","publishedAt":"2018-12-03T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"33.9 g","fat":"23.1 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"9.9 g","calories":"1633 kJ \/ 391 kcal"},"usefulItems":"cling film, large frying pan, large bowl, hob, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["A rich and comforting stew full of flavour. Stews are great to make in the Thermomix® as the meat is constantly stirred while cooking, resulting in a melt-in-the-mouth dish. Serve over polenta for an easy, crowd-pleasing meal."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","26h 15m","8 portions"]}